1
00:01:23,104 --> 00:01:30,560
<i>[Weaving A Tale of Love 2]</i>

2
00:01:32,036 --> 00:01:36,000
<i>[Episode 1]</i>

3
00:01:39,572 --> 00:01:41,492
<i>During the Zhenguan era of the Tang Dynasty,</i>

4
00:01:42,172 --> 00:01:44,312
<i>Lady An,
master tailor of the previous dynasty</i>

5
00:01:44,312 --> 00:01:47,252
<i>[Ruyi Fabric Printing Shop]</i>
<i>lived a low-key life, avoiding fame and wealth,</i>

6
00:01:48,172 --> 00:01:52,252
<i>They had a daughter, Liuli,
who is very intelligent,</i>

7
00:01:52,892 --> 00:01:56,212
<i>[Bureau of Garment]</i>
<i>However, their peaceful life was disrupted</i>

8
00:01:56,212 --> 00:01:59,452
<i>by Lady Zhuojin,
who aspired to be the next master tailor,</i>

9
00:02:01,012 --> 00:02:04,212
<i>Find your master or beheaded,</i>

10
00:02:04,892 --> 00:02:05,972
<i>Make your decision,</i>

11
00:02:06,692 --> 00:02:10,512
<i>[Forensic Bureau]</i>
<i>Lady An had to entrust their daughter</i>

12
00:02:10,512 --> 00:02:14,172
<i>to their friend Sun Decheng,
the Director of the Forensic Bureau,</i>

13
00:02:18,772 --> 00:02:22,452
<i>As Sun's step daughter,
Liuli disguised herself as a man,</i>

14
00:02:22,452 --> 00:02:24,872
<i>and changed her name to Doctor Bean,</i>

15
00:02:24,872 --> 00:02:25,952
<i>Doctor Bean,</i>

16
00:02:26,452 --> 00:02:28,412
<i>how can you be so rude in front of a concubine?</i>

17
00:02:28,412 --> 00:02:30,532
<i>She is the Wu sister who saved me before,</i>

18
00:02:30,532 --> 00:02:32,292
<i>She's a good person, she won't harm me,</i>

19
00:02:35,092 --> 00:02:39,292
<i>My master was the best tailor in the world,
Master An,</i>

20
00:02:40,212 --> 00:02:44,412
<i>Ten years had passed,
her talent was hard to conceal,</i>

21
00:02:45,092 --> 00:02:47,472
<i>The casual embroidery made by Liuli</i>

22
00:02:47,472 --> 00:02:49,932
<i>revealed her tailoring skills of Lady An</i>

23
00:02:49,932 --> 00:02:52,000
<i>to Lady Zhuojin,</i>

24
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:52,452
<i>[Ancestral Tablets of Lady An]</i>

25
00:02:52,452 --> 00:02:55,232
<i>I must find the source of these pouches,</i>

26
00:02:55,232 --> 00:02:56,452
<i>Only then can I be at ease,</i>

27
00:02:57,212 --> 00:03:00,692
<i>Could Director Sun give Doctor Bean to me?</i>

28
00:03:00,692 --> 00:03:03,332
<i>Fearing that the past incident</i>

29
00:03:03,332 --> 00:03:05,152
<i>might put Liuli's life in danger,</i>

30
00:03:05,152 --> 00:03:07,852
<i>Sun Decheng decided to
help Liuli escape from the palace,</i>

31
00:03:11,092 --> 00:03:14,816
<i>Father, Liuli will never forget</i>

32
00:03:15,648 --> 00:03:17,892
<i>your kindness,</i>

33
00:03:18,412 --> 00:03:20,512
<i>When I am not by your side,</i>

34
00:03:20,512 --> 00:03:22,252
<i>you must take care of yourself,</i>

35
00:03:23,732 --> 00:03:25,212
<i>Keep on living,</i>

36
00:03:27,172 --> 00:03:28,972
<i>I heard that Liuli was not dead at all,</i>

37
00:03:28,972 --> 00:03:30,252
<i>and was living well in the palace,</i>

38
00:03:30,772 --> 00:03:33,092
Liuli, we are a family,

39
00:03:33,092 --> 00:03:34,452
We should help each other,

40
00:03:34,452 --> 00:03:35,972
You can't go in, young lady,

41
00:03:35,972 --> 00:03:39,296
<i>[Scholar's Hall]</i>
Pei Xingjian, give back my cousin's belongings!

42
00:03:39,296 --> 00:03:40,392
Didn't I give them back to you?

43
00:03:40,392 --> 00:03:41,572
Don't tell me

44
00:03:41,572 --> 00:03:43,412
the relics of my cousin are these?

45
00:03:44,132 --> 00:03:47,092
She is causing a scene and talking nonsense,

46
00:03:47,092 --> 00:03:49,972
The easiest way is to throw her out,

47
00:03:50,892 --> 00:03:54,272
I can't do anything to you,
but the Hedong Duke's son can,

48
00:03:54,272 --> 00:03:55,932
<i>[General's Mansion]</i>
He has sent people to check your identity,

49
00:03:56,572 --> 00:03:58,732
And will probably find you sooner or later,

50
00:03:58,732 --> 00:04:00,812
<i>[Chonghua Mansion]</i>
Although I found your package,

51
00:04:00,812 --> 00:04:02,972
I haven't opened it just to avoid suspicion,

52
00:04:03,812 --> 00:04:04,892
Hurry up and take it off,

53
00:04:07,412 --> 00:04:09,652
It's obviously a setup of you and your brother,

54
00:04:09,652 --> 00:04:11,892
Trying to deceive some dumbass,
and exact a large sum from him,

55
00:04:17,532 --> 00:04:20,412
Are you the doctor on the warrant or not?

56
00:04:22,452 --> 00:04:25,712
Yes, I'm the wanted doctor, Doctor Bean,

57
00:04:25,712 --> 00:04:27,832
I am also the girl you knew,
by the name of Jade,

58
00:04:27,832 --> 00:04:29,452
Which one is the real you?

59
00:04:31,292 --> 00:04:32,384
What's wrong with me?

60
00:04:34,932 --> 00:04:38,212
Why am I so worried about
that smart and mysterious girl?

61
00:04:38,812 --> 00:04:43,132
<i>She met Pei Xingjian of Hong Wen Pavilion
through misunderstandings,</i>

62
00:04:43,132 --> 00:04:44,632
<i>And with his help,</i>

63
00:04:44,632 --> 00:04:47,172
<i>she won the recognition
of the Chamber of Commerce</i>

64
00:04:47,172 --> 00:04:50,212
with her creative, new-style dance skirt,

65
00:04:50,212 --> 00:04:53,732
Did I blame Pei Xingjian wrongly?

66
00:04:53,732 --> 00:04:56,912
<i>Pei Xingjian fell for innocent and smart Liuli,</i>

67
00:04:56,912 --> 00:05:01,092
<i>[Ruyi Shop]</i>
<i>and she valued his integrity and talent, too,</i>

68
00:05:01,972 --> 00:05:03,512
<i>At this moment…</i>

69
00:05:03,512 --> 00:05:05,952
<i>[Fragrance Shop]</i>
If Little Bean really escaped the Palace,

70
00:05:05,952 --> 00:05:11,372
Sun Decheng'll definitely
try to see her this time,

71
00:05:12,372 --> 00:05:14,992
Damn, She must have gone to see Director Sun,

72
00:05:14,992 --> 00:05:16,132
Where could they meet?

73
00:05:16,132 --> 00:05:17,412
I saw Doctor Bean,

74
00:05:17,412 --> 00:05:19,732
<i>[Arrest warrant]</i>
It's her, Doctor Bean of Forensic Bureau,

75
00:05:19,732 --> 00:05:23,412
<i>Sun Decheng was arrested
for helping Liuli escape the palace,</i>

76
00:05:23,412 --> 00:05:27,612
<i>After knowing that,
Liuli chose to go back to the palace,</i>

77
00:05:27,612 --> 00:05:28,800
I want to turn myself in,

78
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:29,920
Stop the nonsense,

79
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:31,612
I can't let them take the fall for me,

80
00:05:31,612 --> 00:05:32,972
I want to go back and save them,

81
00:05:32,972 --> 00:05:35,332
<i>Pei Xingjian admired her courage,</i>

82
00:05:35,332 --> 00:05:38,692
<i>and entrusted a very important task to her,</i>

83
00:05:39,732 --> 00:05:41,612
There might be a battle in the palace,

84
00:05:42,212 --> 00:05:44,892
Remember, keep your distance from Prince Cao,

85
00:05:46,012 --> 00:05:47,172
Someone tries to murder Prince,

86
00:05:47,172 --> 00:05:49,012
<i>Pei Xingjian secretly investigated Prince Cao,</i>

87
00:05:49,012 --> 00:05:52,012
<i>he found out
Prince Cao had smuggled a batch of armor,</i>

88
00:05:53,652 --> 00:05:54,972
<i>Pei Xingjian wanted Liuli to</i>

89
00:05:54,972 --> 00:05:58,372
<i>manage to send important news to prince
in the palace,</i>

90
00:05:58,372 --> 00:06:00,772
<i>and prevented Prince Cao
from secretly transporting those armor,</i>

91
00:06:02,252 --> 00:06:05,252
<i>With his extraordinary courage and strategy,</i>

92
00:06:05,252 --> 00:06:07,892
<i>Pei Xingjian was promoted to be
a personal guard for the prince,</i>

93
00:06:08,412 --> 00:06:11,972
<i>while Liuli found out Lady Zhuojin
had something to do with her mother's death,</i>

94
00:06:11,972 --> 00:06:14,812
<i>Then, she decided to
investigate the Bureau of Shangfu,</i>

95
00:06:14,812 --> 00:06:16,172
Is that woman Lady Zhuojin?

96
00:06:18,172 --> 00:06:22,172
Back then,
my master was the best tailor in the world,

97
00:06:22,172 --> 00:06:26,292
She's in charge of the Bureau of Shangfu,
renowned throughout the country,

98
00:06:26,292 --> 00:06:30,752
But she ended up with a broken family
and a ruined reputation,

99
00:06:30,752 --> 00:06:33,132
couldn't even protect her own daughter,

100
00:06:41,696 --> 00:06:42,784
<i>[Spring Workshop]</i>

101
00:06:42,784 --> 00:06:47,092
Mother, I will retrieve your golden needle

102
00:06:47,092 --> 00:06:48,772
and your reputation tomorrow,

103
00:06:49,612 --> 00:06:50,688
Why are you here?

104
00:06:56,092 --> 00:06:57,120
What are you doing?

105
00:06:58,292 --> 00:07:00,532
Measuring your waist for sure,
What else could I be doing?

106
00:07:01,212 --> 00:07:02,732
Remember not to indulge in drinking like this
in the future,

107
00:07:03,772 --> 00:07:06,172
Don't forget that you are a lady,

108
00:07:06,172 --> 00:07:07,264
Little Bean,

109
00:07:12,812 --> 00:07:13,888
Prove it,

110
00:07:14,892 --> 00:07:16,532
Prove whether or not I am truly a man,

111
00:07:16,532 --> 00:07:19,212
You're not a man, you are a saint, a gentleman,

112
00:07:22,332 --> 00:07:23,532
You can always trust me,

113
00:07:24,172 --> 00:07:27,452
Perhaps not just in this moment,

114
00:07:28,292 --> 00:07:31,452
It might have started a long time ago,

115
00:07:32,372 --> 00:07:35,972
<i>They took care of each other in the palace,
and their hearts connected,</i>

116
00:07:36,532 --> 00:07:40,192
<i>Pei Xingjian secretly helped Liuli
investigate the old case,</i>

117
00:07:40,192 --> 00:07:43,052
<i>He discovered
it's Lady Zhuojin who poisoned Lady An,</i>

118
00:07:43,052 --> 00:07:47,092
<i>He found that
their love had begun ten years ago,</i>

119
00:07:47,092 --> 00:07:48,252
<i>He still kept</i>

120
00:07:48,252 --> 00:07:51,032
<i>the belongings of Lady An
that Liuli left behind in her panic,</i>

121
00:07:51,032 --> 00:07:53,132
<i>The golden needle,</i>

122
00:07:53,132 --> 00:07:54,572
I have been looking for you for 11 years,

123
00:07:55,292 --> 00:07:57,212
I never thought you'd already be by my side,

124
00:07:57,212 --> 00:07:58,492
We really are fated,

125
00:07:58,492 --> 00:07:59,892
Finally, I can return it to its rightful owner,

126
00:08:08,532 --> 00:08:10,872
Little Bean's sewing skills

127
00:08:10,872 --> 00:08:13,692
could really come from my master,

128
00:08:14,332 --> 00:08:16,012
<i>At this moment, Lady Zhuojin</i>

129
00:08:16,012 --> 00:08:18,332
<i>began to suspect Liuli's identity,</i>

130
00:08:19,092 --> 00:08:22,892
<i>Facing this crisis,
Pei Xingjian offered up the golden needle</i>

131
00:08:22,892 --> 00:08:26,572
<i>[Liuli's memorial tablet]</i>
<i>to dispel Lady Zhuojin's doubts,</i>

132
00:08:31,132 --> 00:08:35,412
This is the golden needle
that represents the best tailor in the world,

133
00:08:36,012 --> 00:08:37,132
- Liuli,
- Let go of me,

134
00:08:38,652 --> 00:08:40,612
I can't do it,

135
00:08:41,292 --> 00:08:45,252
I can't give away my mother's needle
to the enemy who killed her,

136
00:08:45,252 --> 00:08:47,972
This causes me more pain than death itself,

137
00:08:49,172 --> 00:08:53,472
<i>The golden needle
caused a rift between Pei Xingjian and Liuli,</i>

138
00:08:53,472 --> 00:08:56,132
<i>Liuli could not forgive Pei Xingjian,</i>

139
00:09:00,372 --> 00:09:01,712
I don't want to see you,

140
00:09:01,712 --> 00:09:05,652
Doctor Bean is suffering from
injuries and heartache at the same time,

141
00:09:05,652 --> 00:09:08,052
She said she never wanted to see you again,

142
00:09:08,812 --> 00:09:10,792
Liuli, what happened to your leg?

143
00:09:10,792 --> 00:09:13,212
This is my business, leave me alone,

144
00:09:14,012 --> 00:09:18,052
You prayed for a bad draw
in front of the Buddha,

145
00:09:18,572 --> 00:09:21,052
I secretly turned it back twice,

146
00:09:21,052 --> 00:09:22,872
that's why you got the best draw in the end,

147
00:09:22,872 --> 00:09:23,968
What are you saying?

148
00:09:26,612 --> 00:09:30,852
Little Bean, you and I really are fated,

149
00:09:39,932 --> 00:09:42,092
You truly are a beauty in the making,

150
00:09:43,612 --> 00:09:44,752
Little Bean is missing!

151
00:09:44,752 --> 00:09:48,092
Maybe Prince Cao and Mistress Yang
took her away,

152
00:09:48,892 --> 00:09:50,144
<i>Liuli could not bear to see</i>

153
00:09:50,144 --> 00:09:52,892
<i>the murderer who framed her mother succeed,</i>

154
00:09:52,892 --> 00:09:54,912
<i>Yet she herself was poisoned,</i>

155
00:09:54,912 --> 00:09:56,572
I'm also looking for the antidote,

156
00:09:57,652 --> 00:09:59,412
But this poison has no antidote,

157
00:10:00,092 --> 00:10:02,532
I fully understand
the pain she is going through now,

158
00:10:03,732 --> 00:10:07,332
Even if it costs my life, I will cure you,

159
00:10:07,332 --> 00:10:08,384
Pei Xingjian,

160
00:10:09,892 --> 00:10:11,572
Don't you understand?

161
00:10:13,452 --> 00:10:14,464
I'm not afraid to die,

162
00:10:15,492 --> 00:10:17,092
My fear is until death,

163
00:10:17,092 --> 00:10:19,492
mother's case still can't come to light,

164
00:10:19,492 --> 00:10:21,092
Her title of the best tailor in the world,

165
00:10:21,092 --> 00:10:22,692
is still usurped by her murderer,

166
00:10:25,172 --> 00:10:28,132
As long as
we find the herb called "Cliff Linglong Vine",

167
00:10:28,932 --> 00:10:30,292
I will definitely be able to cure you,

168
00:10:32,852 --> 00:10:34,092
This is my personal belonging,

169
00:10:35,732 --> 00:10:37,932
Let it be with you for me,

170
00:10:39,052 --> 00:10:40,132
Wait for me to come back,

171
00:10:46,852 --> 00:10:50,332
<i>In this critical moment,
Pei Xingjian risked his life,</i>

172
00:10:50,332 --> 00:10:53,892
<i>using his wit to get the antidote,
and saved Liuli,</i>

173
00:10:54,492 --> 00:10:57,932
<i>Then they got over their past
and worked together to resolve the crisis,</i>

174
00:10:58,652 --> 00:10:59,812
I know from my heart,

175
00:11:01,852 --> 00:11:07,332
Pei Xingjian, I couldn't ask for more
with him being in my life,

176
00:11:08,932 --> 00:11:10,292
I don't want just be with you this moment,

177
00:11:12,172 --> 00:11:13,572
I want to be with you forever,

178
00:11:18,532 --> 00:11:21,992
<i>Emperor Taizong died
and Prince Li Zhi ascended the throne,</i>

179
00:11:21,992 --> 00:11:25,732
<i>Lady An was exonerated,
and Lady Zhuojin got what she deserved,</i>

180
00:11:27,012 --> 00:11:29,952
<i>[Judgement]</i>
The case is definite and the evidence is solid,

181
00:11:29,952 --> 00:11:32,532
The crime is unforgivable,

182
00:11:36,132 --> 00:11:38,292
Liuli, I don't want to die,

183
00:11:39,852 --> 00:11:44,452
Let me go, please, Liuli, I can't die,

184
00:11:44,452 --> 00:11:48,212
<i>Liuli and Pei Xingjian, after all these,
they love each other with all their hearts,</i>

185
00:11:48,932 --> 00:11:52,212
<i>Emperor Gaozong appreciated their friendship,
he granted their marriage,</i>

186
00:11:54,292 --> 00:11:56,452
<i>Pei Xingjian married Liuli</i>

187
00:11:56,452 --> 00:11:58,532
<i>under the blessing of</i>

188
00:11:58,532 --> 00:12:01,212
<i>his mentor Su Dingfang, and all his friends,</i>

189
00:12:01,892 --> 00:12:03,292
Do you know how hard it has been for me?

190
00:12:04,732 --> 00:12:06,292
It's hard for me when I can't see you,

191
00:12:07,692 --> 00:12:10,772
It's even harder when I see you,

192
00:12:15,652 --> 00:12:18,892
<i>They were happily married with each other,</i>

193
00:12:19,692 --> 00:12:23,132
<i>However,
the joy of the wedding had not yet dissipated,</i>

194
00:12:23,132 --> 00:12:27,132
<i>[Act on kindness]</i>
<i>a bigger crisis had already come,</i>

195
00:12:32,836 --> 00:12:35,712
<i>[Chang'an]</i>

196
00:12:57,988 --> 00:13:00,992
<i>[Residence of the Hedong Duke]</i>

197
00:13:01,700 --> 00:13:05,024
<i>[Residence of the Hedong Duke]</i>

198
00:13:47,140 --> 00:13:50,816
<i>[Princess Linhai, wife of the Hedong Duke]</i>

199
00:14:18,436 --> 00:14:20,512
<i>[Princess Linhai's elder daughter in law,
Lady Cui]</i>

200
00:14:20,512 --> 00:14:22,692
<i>[Princess Linhai's younger daughter in law,
Lady Lu]</i>

201
00:14:22,692 --> 00:14:27,252
Although it was a bit of trouble
to find the person you ordered, madam,

202
00:14:27,252 --> 00:14:29,892
I've found someone,

203
00:14:29,892 --> 00:14:33,232
Please check whether she fits or not, madam,

204
00:14:33,232 --> 00:14:35,452
This woman's name is Yunu,

205
00:14:36,612 --> 00:14:38,732
Greetings, princess,

206
00:14:59,212 --> 00:15:02,212
She looks so similar, she really does,

207
00:15:02,932 --> 00:15:08,292
Cui, you did a great job on this,

208
00:15:08,292 --> 00:15:09,568
Thank you, madam,

209
00:15:09,568 --> 00:15:10,592
Lu,

210
00:15:11,452 --> 00:15:13,972
has there been any thing on Pei Shouyue?

211
00:15:14,772 --> 00:15:15,812
Madam,

212
00:15:16,812 --> 00:15:20,092
Pei Shouyue and the new bride
are truly in love and harmony,

213
00:15:20,092 --> 00:15:23,012
The new house I gave them,

214
00:15:23,612 --> 00:15:25,792
I wonder if they are satisfied with it,

215
00:15:25,792 --> 00:15:27,572
Madam, you played your cards well,

216
00:15:27,572 --> 00:15:30,292
Although
Pei Shouyue is the eldest son of Pei family,

217
00:15:30,292 --> 00:15:32,812
he couldn't dare to refuse the gift from you,

218
00:15:33,492 --> 00:15:36,052
Moreover, it is said that

219
00:15:36,052 --> 00:15:39,292
Pei Shouyue
has been secretly looking for a new house,

220
00:15:39,292 --> 00:15:41,732
It seems he wants to move as soon as possible,

221
00:15:41,732 --> 00:15:42,932
Secretly?

222
00:15:45,412 --> 00:15:49,772
I'm sure he is keeping this from his new wife,

223
00:15:50,892 --> 00:15:55,452
Since Liuli doesn't know story of the house,

224
00:15:57,212 --> 00:15:59,092
Let Yunu catch her up,

225
00:16:02,884 --> 00:16:05,504
<i>[Residence of the county magistrate of Chang'an
Pei Xingjian]</i>

226
00:16:08,332 --> 00:16:09,852
Come on, everyone, pull yourself together,

227
00:16:10,412 --> 00:16:14,212
Today is the first court session
after the master's wedding,

228
00:16:14,212 --> 00:16:16,384
Let's do everything thoroughly and efficiently,

229
00:16:16,384 --> 00:16:17,472
Alright,

230
00:16:17,472 --> 00:16:18,932
Be joyful,

231
00:16:18,932 --> 00:16:21,172
Bring good luck to the master and lady,

232
00:16:21,172 --> 00:16:22,176
Okay,

233
00:16:24,012 --> 00:16:26,732
<i>[Pei Mansion]</i>
The maid princess Linhai sent is here,

234
00:16:30,212 --> 00:16:32,012
Come and greet her, servants!

235
00:16:42,852 --> 00:16:45,692
Cheng, what are you staring at
early in the morning?

236
00:16:46,692 --> 00:16:47,892
Am I seeing the ghosts?

237
00:16:49,452 --> 00:16:52,292
Don't talk nonsense,
The master and lady are newly wedded,

238
00:16:52,292 --> 00:16:53,572
Do not talk about these bad things,

239
00:16:54,492 --> 00:16:56,612
Right, sister, you are correct,

240
00:16:56,612 --> 00:16:59,052
Today is the first court session
after the master's wedding,

241
00:16:59,892 --> 00:17:01,192
Sister, you stay home with her,

242
00:17:01,192 --> 00:17:03,412
Try to avoid the backyard,

243
00:17:03,972 --> 00:17:05,024
Why not?

244
00:17:05,852 --> 00:17:06,972
Sister, don't ask too much,

245
00:17:06,972 --> 00:17:09,872
By the way,
master has ordered me to look for a new house,

246
00:17:09,872 --> 00:17:12,452
Once the place is decided,
master will tell her himself,

247
00:17:13,612 --> 00:17:16,092
So don't gossip in front of the lady,

248
00:17:37,028 --> 00:17:39,168
<i>[Wife of Pei Xingjian, Kudi Liuli]</i>

249
00:17:49,796 --> 00:17:53,856
<i>[County magistrate of Chang'an, Pei Xingjian,
named Shouyue]</i>

250
00:17:54,724 --> 00:17:55,616
<i>[Follow Benevolence and Justice]</i>

251
00:18:08,732 --> 00:18:10,132
Did you sleep well last night?

252
00:18:13,772 --> 00:18:15,132
Who is playing the flute?

253
00:18:16,012 --> 00:18:17,712
It's really beautiful,

254
00:18:17,712 --> 00:18:19,372
But the song is somewhat sad,

255
00:18:20,012 --> 00:18:21,184
You keep sleeping,

256
00:18:21,792 --> 00:18:24,852
I will check out which rude servant is this,

257
00:18:24,852 --> 00:18:26,972
and tell them not to disturb your rest,

258
00:18:28,172 --> 00:18:30,812
Just send Ni over,

259
00:18:30,812 --> 00:18:32,292
There's no need for you to go,

260
00:18:32,292 --> 00:18:34,132
Ni just moved here with you,

261
00:18:34,132 --> 00:18:36,092
She's not yet familiar with the servants,

262
00:18:37,212 --> 00:18:38,332
I'll send Cheng instead,

263
00:18:39,332 --> 00:18:40,384
That works,

264
00:19:09,572 --> 00:19:10,792
My lady is up,

265
00:19:10,792 --> 00:19:13,612
Ni, where is this flute sound coming from?

266
00:19:13,612 --> 00:19:16,012
It seems to be the back garden,

267
00:19:16,012 --> 00:19:18,340
<i>[Jiayi Hall]</i>

268
00:19:26,724 --> 00:19:29,888
<i>[Wandering Cloud]</i>

269
00:19:31,292 --> 00:19:32,416
Cheng,

270
00:19:33,052 --> 00:19:34,152
Greetings, my lady,

271
00:19:34,152 --> 00:19:36,212
Do you know who was playing the flute
in the garden?

272
00:19:38,572 --> 00:19:40,252
Maybe a thoughtless maid,

273
00:19:41,052 --> 00:19:42,852
She disturbed my lady and master,

274
00:19:43,372 --> 00:19:45,732
Don't worry about it, my lady,
I will stop it right away,

275
00:19:45,732 --> 00:19:47,732
It's just a song,

276
00:19:47,732 --> 00:19:50,332
Why are you and Shouyue so nervous?

277
00:19:51,812 --> 00:19:55,892
I'm just worried she will be a trouble,

278
00:19:55,892 --> 00:19:57,412
Won't you tell the truth?

279
00:19:57,412 --> 00:19:59,252
Then I would like to see it for myself,

280
00:20:00,372 --> 00:20:01,408
But…

281
00:20:23,492 --> 00:20:26,972
Who are you? How dare you be so reckless here!

282
00:21:02,492 --> 00:21:03,532
<i>Lady Luqi,</i>

283
00:21:12,740 --> 00:21:13,920
<i>[Happiness]</i>

284
00:21:23,852 --> 00:21:25,832
Why did the flute stop suddenly?

285
00:21:25,832 --> 00:21:28,332
My lady, please have breakfast with master,

286
00:21:28,332 --> 00:21:29,812
Let me handle this,

287
00:21:41,292 --> 00:21:43,132
Greetings, master,

288
00:21:44,452 --> 00:21:47,132
Are you the one who sent by the princess?

289
00:22:02,372 --> 00:22:03,492
My lady, please don't get the wrong idea,

290
00:22:04,492 --> 00:22:06,032
It's not what you think,

291
00:22:06,032 --> 00:22:09,252
Then, you should tell me the truth,

292
00:22:09,812 --> 00:22:13,612
Cheng, is she an old acquaintance of Shouyue?

293
00:22:14,612 --> 00:22:18,452
My lady, master and Yunu
did not know each other before,

294
00:22:19,212 --> 00:22:22,812
Just… I don't know where did the princess

295
00:22:22,812 --> 00:22:24,332
find such a person

296
00:22:25,772 --> 00:22:28,212
looks so similar to Lady Luqi,

297
00:22:28,852 --> 00:22:31,472
even her flute is quite similar,

298
00:22:31,472 --> 00:22:34,692
Yunu looks like the ex-wife of the master?

299
00:22:39,132 --> 00:22:42,892
I'm just a poor woman
who can't control her own fate,

300
00:22:43,772 --> 00:22:49,372
Now I'm here,
the only one I can rely on is master,

301
00:22:50,572 --> 00:22:52,572
I heard that the master and Lady Luqi

302
00:22:53,172 --> 00:22:56,292
once were very in love,

303
00:22:56,812 --> 00:23:01,932
After Lady Luqi died,
master felt guilty and missed her very much,

304
00:23:03,372 --> 00:23:06,212
I wish to take the place of Lady Luqi,

305
00:23:09,012 --> 00:23:10,052
to comfort master,

306
00:23:16,052 --> 00:23:17,852
Princess really knows her tactics,

307
00:23:22,412 --> 00:23:25,252
Ni, where is Yunu's contract?

308
00:23:25,252 --> 00:23:28,492
It hasn't been sent here,
What will you do with it?

309
00:23:29,452 --> 00:23:31,852
Are you going to sell her?

310
00:23:31,852 --> 00:23:34,892
My lady, this must not happen,

311
00:23:36,172 --> 00:23:38,532
Princess said she sent her as a maid,

312
00:23:38,532 --> 00:23:40,652
but actually, she is kind of a lady,

313
00:23:42,252 --> 00:23:44,572
We must keep her here, how dare we sell her?

314
00:23:45,332 --> 00:23:48,072
Besides, even if we want to sell,
I'm afraid no one would dare to take her,

315
00:23:48,072 --> 00:23:49,252
Who said I'm going to sell her?

316
00:23:50,812 --> 00:23:51,812
Then, what do you want to do?

317
00:23:52,932 --> 00:23:56,052
As a new bride, I should

318
00:23:56,052 --> 00:23:57,732
pay our respect to the princess with Shouyue,

319
00:24:10,336 --> 00:24:11,452
<i>[Lotus Pavilion]</i>

320
00:24:11,452 --> 00:24:13,292
Greetings, princess,

321
00:24:14,092 --> 00:24:16,172
Liuli pays her respects to the princess,

322
00:24:16,932 --> 00:24:18,048
Please, have a seat,

323
00:24:19,452 --> 00:24:22,692
Yunu? Why are you here?

324
00:24:22,692 --> 00:24:24,372
Princess,

325
00:24:24,932 --> 00:24:26,048
on that day, Lady Cui

326
00:24:26,048 --> 00:24:28,792
brought this beautiful woman to visit my home,

327
00:24:28,792 --> 00:24:31,412
and she forgot to take Yunu with her,

328
00:24:32,092 --> 00:24:35,272
Thinking that I would drop by,

329
00:24:35,272 --> 00:24:38,652
so, I let her stay at my house for a few days,

330
00:24:38,652 --> 00:24:40,892
Today, I brought her back to you,

331
00:24:46,972 --> 00:24:50,012
Cui, what's the matter?

332
00:24:50,732 --> 00:24:55,192
She misunderstood,
That day I made it very clear,

333
00:24:55,192 --> 00:24:57,452
that Yunu was given to Shouyue and Kudi

334
00:24:57,452 --> 00:24:59,832
as a maid by your ladyship,

335
00:24:59,832 --> 00:25:02,092
I even instructed Yunu

336
00:25:02,092 --> 00:25:04,932
to serve the master and lady well,

337
00:25:06,932 --> 00:25:09,892
Could it be you've forgotten?

338
00:25:12,132 --> 00:25:14,452
I'm sorry for that,

339
00:25:15,252 --> 00:25:18,192
It's just that
Lady Cui forgot to leave her contract

340
00:25:18,192 --> 00:25:19,892
when she sent Yunu over,

341
00:25:20,452 --> 00:25:23,052
So, I just thought

342
00:25:23,052 --> 00:25:26,112
"it only right to send the maid
and her contract over",

343
00:25:26,112 --> 00:25:27,292
So, I got confused,

344
00:25:36,052 --> 00:25:37,056
Cui,

345
00:25:38,132 --> 00:25:40,272
what exactly are you doing?

346
00:25:40,272 --> 00:25:43,412
I knew you were just careless,

347
00:25:43,412 --> 00:25:46,972
but others would think
I was being mean on purpose,

348
00:25:47,852 --> 00:25:51,172
Go and fetch Yunu's contract,

349
00:25:58,972 --> 00:26:00,064
Yes,

350
00:26:09,732 --> 00:26:12,532
<i>The princess was pressured by Kudi</i>

351
00:26:12,532 --> 00:26:13,692
<i>and had no choice but to say so,</i>

352
00:26:14,372 --> 00:26:16,512
<i>If I were to actually hand over her contract,</i>

353
00:26:16,512 --> 00:26:18,172
<i>she would definitely vent her anger on me,</i>

354
00:26:18,172 --> 00:26:19,612
<i>What should I do?</i>

355
00:26:30,732 --> 00:26:33,332
Madam, pardon me,

356
00:26:33,332 --> 00:26:36,572
I mixed up her contract with other documents,

357
00:26:37,932 --> 00:26:39,252
leaving it at another estate,

358
00:26:42,532 --> 00:26:43,852
I've already ordered someone to fetch it,

359
00:26:43,852 --> 00:26:46,692
and as soon as it's retrieved,
I will immediately send it to Lady Liuli,

360
00:26:46,692 --> 00:26:48,372
Thank you, Lady Cui,

361
00:26:50,452 --> 00:26:52,572
And thank you, princess,

362
00:26:52,572 --> 00:26:55,572
I shall accept Yunu as a generous gift,

363
00:26:56,292 --> 00:26:57,692
Lady Liuli knows the proper etiquette,

364
00:26:58,252 --> 00:27:01,452
The younger
shouldn't refuse the gift from the elder,

365
00:27:02,132 --> 00:27:07,572
And the younger shouldn't hit, scold

366
00:27:08,292 --> 00:27:10,892
sold, or abuse the maid who is a gift,

367
00:27:17,052 --> 00:27:19,732
I couldn't afford the princess to say so,

368
00:27:20,292 --> 00:27:22,712
Someone as delicate as Yunu,

369
00:27:22,712 --> 00:27:26,972
me and Shouyue will be loathed
to part with her,

370
00:28:00,852 --> 00:28:02,252
Where to go?

371
00:28:02,252 --> 00:28:04,792
That tramp is playing her flute again,
trying to seduce master,

372
00:28:04,792 --> 00:28:08,052
I know my lady upholds dignity
and doesn't bother to give a fuss,

373
00:28:08,052 --> 00:28:09,572
I'll go and punish her for you,

374
00:28:09,572 --> 00:28:10,624
No,

375
00:28:34,692 --> 00:28:37,292
Why did she stop all of a sudden?

376
00:28:37,292 --> 00:28:40,692
My lady,
could it be that master really went to see her?

377
00:28:41,252 --> 00:28:44,972
Otherwise, why would she stop right there?

378
00:28:48,252 --> 00:28:49,452
She plays the flute all day long,

379
00:28:50,252 --> 00:28:52,132
but doesn't expect master to come see her,

380
00:28:53,412 --> 00:28:56,692
She just wants to sabotage our relationship,

381
00:28:58,572 --> 00:28:59,652
For example,

382
00:29:00,332 --> 00:29:03,152
she plays the flute, you let your mind wander,

383
00:29:03,152 --> 00:29:06,492
when she stops, you still let your mind wander,

384
00:29:08,692 --> 00:29:09,772
In the long run,

385
00:29:12,212 --> 00:29:15,092
misunderstandings and estrangements
will inevitably arise between the couple,

386
00:29:15,092 --> 00:29:17,192
Since you have already seen through her tricks,

387
00:29:17,192 --> 00:29:18,892
do not let her spoil your mood,

388
00:29:21,052 --> 00:29:23,492
The most vicious thing of psywar is

389
00:29:23,492 --> 00:29:26,572
even after seeing through the tricks,
the misunderstanding still exists,

390
00:29:28,292 --> 00:29:31,532
As long as I love Shouyue,
there will be jealousy,

391
00:29:32,332 --> 00:29:34,372
Where there is jealousy,
there will be suspicion,

392
00:29:34,892 --> 00:29:37,132
Where there is suspicion,
there will be an estrangement,

393
00:29:38,012 --> 00:29:42,452
The saying goes, "care leads to confusion",

394
00:29:46,308 --> 00:29:48,384
<i>[Harmony and Steadfastness]</i>

395
00:29:59,456 --> 00:30:00,512
Cheng,

396
00:30:00,512 --> 00:30:01,532
Yes,

397
00:30:01,532 --> 00:30:02,692
Did you put this flower here?

398
00:30:03,572 --> 00:30:05,332
No, master, it's not me,

399
00:30:05,892 --> 00:30:06,932
I did,

400
00:30:10,628 --> 00:30:12,416
<i>[Harmony and Steadfastness]</i>

401
00:30:15,652 --> 00:30:16,932
Greetings, master,

402
00:30:17,892 --> 00:30:20,632
I brought the michelia figo here,

403
00:30:20,632 --> 00:30:22,752
for the master and lady to enjoy,

404
00:30:22,752 --> 00:30:27,132
It's delicate and pleasant to smell,

405
00:30:27,812 --> 00:30:29,572
Furthermore, I overheard

406
00:30:29,572 --> 00:30:33,252
Lady Luqi loved it a lot when she was alive,

407
00:30:36,972 --> 00:30:41,092
And she wore herself out for Pei family,

408
00:30:41,692 --> 00:30:44,772
<i>[Harmony and Steadfastness]</i>
The master has always felt guilty to her,

409
00:30:45,572 --> 00:30:47,292
Therefore, I put it here,

410
00:30:48,252 --> 00:30:51,692
to appease master's longing for her,

411
00:30:54,332 --> 00:30:56,852
Kudi Liuli, though she is a barbarian woman,

412
00:30:57,972 --> 00:31:00,612
Still, she used to be an official in the palace

413
00:31:00,612 --> 00:31:02,812
<i>[Treasures fill the home]</i>
and as a head of Bureau of Garment,

414
00:31:03,892 --> 00:31:08,332
So, she is much cleverer than Lady Luqi,

415
00:31:09,372 --> 00:31:13,092
Even if Lady Liuli has some small tricks,

416
00:31:13,732 --> 00:31:15,532
could she even compete with princess?

417
00:31:16,452 --> 00:31:18,652
She will end up in failure,

418
00:31:19,612 --> 00:31:22,492
How much better can she be than Lady Luqi?

419
00:31:23,612 --> 00:31:26,012
In the end, after all…

420
00:31:26,012 --> 00:31:27,040
What?

421
00:31:28,652 --> 00:31:30,872
Lady Luqi's death, what has it to do with me?

422
00:31:30,872 --> 00:31:36,012
Ten years ago,
Shouyue married Lady Luqi on mother's order,

423
00:31:36,012 --> 00:31:39,852
They just wanted me to honor our promise

424
00:31:40,372 --> 00:31:43,572
to return Pei family's fortune
that I had managed for years,

425
00:31:44,092 --> 00:31:48,732
Pei's family was really ruthless,

426
00:31:49,452 --> 00:31:53,372
They fixated on Pei Shouyue's inheritance,

427
00:31:53,372 --> 00:31:55,492
that ultimately drove Lady Luqi to her death,

428
00:31:58,172 --> 00:32:00,972
After all, what does this have to do with me?

429
00:32:02,652 --> 00:32:05,092
Yes, madam, you're right,

430
00:32:05,772 --> 00:32:06,872
You should visit the Pei mansion,

431
00:32:06,872 --> 00:32:08,852
We need to help Yunu do her work,

432
00:32:10,732 --> 00:32:11,904
Yes, madam,

433
00:32:15,372 --> 00:32:17,652
Today, I have come for two matters,

434
00:32:18,172 --> 00:32:21,832
The first is to apologize to you,

435
00:32:21,832 --> 00:32:25,452
Yesterday,
I sent someone to fetch Yunu's contract,

436
00:32:25,452 --> 00:32:28,012
But the residence was burglarized,

437
00:32:28,012 --> 00:32:29,892
Besides gold, silver, and money

438
00:32:29,892 --> 00:32:32,972
the thief also stole Yunu's contract,

439
00:32:36,412 --> 00:32:38,952
There is such a bold thief,

440
00:32:38,952 --> 00:32:41,172
daring to steal from Hedong Duke,

441
00:32:41,172 --> 00:32:43,412
and specifically took Yunu's contract,

442
00:32:45,252 --> 00:32:47,932
In this case, there is no need to hurry,

443
00:32:48,612 --> 00:32:50,144
Once Shouyue catches the thief,

444
00:32:50,144 --> 00:32:53,072
you will naturally get her contract,

445
00:32:53,072 --> 00:32:56,172
I wonder what the second matter is,

446
00:32:59,172 --> 00:33:03,632
Recently, princess feels weak and exhausted,

447
00:33:03,632 --> 00:33:05,372
We called the imperial physician several times,

448
00:33:06,172 --> 00:33:08,932
Madam was thinking of
going to pray and seek blessings at the temple,

449
00:33:09,492 --> 00:33:13,432
Hence, I am here to follow her instructions

450
00:33:13,432 --> 00:33:15,932
to invite you to join us,

451
00:33:15,932 --> 00:33:19,572
Princess wishes for me to accompany her
to the temple for prayers,

452
00:33:20,692 --> 00:33:24,412
You know enough not to refuse

453
00:33:24,412 --> 00:33:26,692
the chance to show filial piety to her, right?

454
00:33:31,692 --> 00:33:33,792
Concerning the well-being of the princess,

455
00:33:33,792 --> 00:33:36,852
if I can offer even a little support,
it would be a blessing I earnestly wish for,

456
00:33:39,652 --> 00:33:42,252
Yunu, princess has treated you very well,

457
00:33:42,252 --> 00:33:45,212
you shall accompany me to serve her,

458
00:33:45,212 --> 00:33:48,612
No, there is no need for Yunu to go,

459
00:33:49,652 --> 00:33:50,720
Why not?

460
00:33:51,572 --> 00:33:53,892
Her birth chart clashes

461
00:33:53,892 --> 00:33:55,132
with that of the Princess,

462
00:33:55,132 --> 00:34:00,732
She can stay here to serve Shouyue for you,

463
00:34:12,532 --> 00:34:15,792
Please take a message to princess for me,
Lady Cui,

464
00:34:15,792 --> 00:34:18,512
I will take good care of my master,

465
00:34:18,512 --> 00:34:20,532
with no negligence whatsoever,

466
00:34:22,972 --> 00:34:24,292
Then, I won't take up any more of your time,

467
00:34:27,772 --> 00:34:30,012
I will come to fetch you tomorrow morning,

468
00:34:30,012 --> 00:34:31,132
Goodbye, Lady Cui,

469
00:34:40,452 --> 00:34:44,012
The fragrance on your body
is sweet but not cloying, with a gentle scent,

470
00:34:44,532 --> 00:34:46,052
I wonder what fragrance you use,

471
00:34:49,012 --> 00:34:51,532
It's indeed special, but it isn't mine,

472
00:34:53,812 --> 00:34:57,372
You must be referring to my fragrance,

473
00:34:57,972 --> 00:34:59,212
My father is a florist,

474
00:34:59,212 --> 00:35:01,792
I've grown up among the flowers,

475
00:35:01,792 --> 00:35:05,412
Many have said I have this unique scent,

476
00:35:06,052 --> 00:35:08,852
it's not from any fragrant powder,

477
00:35:10,012 --> 00:35:11,452
Sorry to make you laugh at me,

478
00:35:16,652 --> 00:35:19,212
Being as pretty as a flower is one thing,

479
00:35:20,012 --> 00:35:21,412
but to also have a natural body scent,

480
00:35:23,372 --> 00:35:26,532
Indeed, a rare beauty in this world,
even I cannot help loving you,

481
00:35:27,172 --> 00:35:31,092
No wonder princess sees you differently,

482
00:35:44,452 --> 00:35:45,372
<i>[Pei Mansion]</i>

483
00:35:45,372 --> 00:35:49,332
Liuli, don't worry,
accompany princess for a few days,

484
00:35:50,892 --> 00:35:52,492
I'll stay in the county office tomorrow night,

485
00:35:53,372 --> 00:35:54,972
I won't give Yunu any chance,

486
00:35:56,532 --> 00:35:59,252
