487
00:35:59,252 --> 00:36:00,412
be very careful,

488
00:36:01,892 --> 00:36:03,252
In order to take our property,

489
00:36:04,092 --> 00:36:05,600
the princess will surely

490
00:36:05,600 --> 00:36:07,492
