491
00:36:08,532 --> 00:36:12,092
Those were indeed left to me
by my father and brothers,

492
00:36:13,212 --> 00:36:14,812
But I would rather give up all those

493
00:36:15,652 --> 00:36:17,332
than to see you hurt in any way,

494
00:36:21,732 --> 00:36:24,812
Shouyue,
I trust that you are completely devoted to me,

495
00:36:25,612 --> 00:36:27,732
