that I can be your good wife,

496
00:36:28,332 --> 00:36:30,892
You are in charge of external affairs,
I am in charge of internal ones,

497
00:36:31,612 --> 00:36:35,172
Just focus on national affairs,
focus on Chang'an county affairs,

498
00:36:35,852 --> 00:36:38,332
Leave the house affairs to me,

499
00:36:43,292 --> 00:36:44,384
Shouyue,

500
00:36:45,892 --> 00:36:48,092
